name: Gan-Nouveau Futurism : Rigil Kentaurus Oracle
description:
Assisted by generative adversarial networks I am scanning the collective cultural subconsciousness. By combining classic art with mythology pop-culture I search for correlations in content and aesthetics that transcend time and location | artist: Bas Uterwijk (@ganbrood)| medium: PNG, 4800x8000 pixels | original creation date:  November 25, 2021 

This Non Fungible Token includes a signed and numbered Epson print on 308gms Hahnemulle matt Photorag fine-art paper (329x483mm) shipped to any global destination.
When reselling the NFT the original print should be shipped in a pristine state to the new owner, where the seller is responsible for proper packaging and shipping costs.
